snippet.title: Exploring Alternatives
snippet.description:
Exploring Alternatives is a hub of alternative living video content that we hope will inform and inspire you.  

Each week, we post a new video about people who are living in tiny houses, vans, RVs, and boats; and people who are exploring long-term travel, minimalism, zero waste living, off-grid living, and more.  

Subscribe to see new videos and let us know what you think in the comments!  

Thanks for watching and happy exploring :)

Mat & Danielle
